1 pod2hlp
pod2hlp
NAME
    pod2hlp - pod to VMS help file reformatter.

SYNOPSIS
    perl pod2hlp podfile

DESCRIPTION
    This program uses the Pod::Hlp module from the Pod2VMSHlp
    package. This program takes a podfile.TYPE and produces a
    reformatted podfile.hlp file in the same directory.

